msgctxt "an3.18:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Rathakāravagga "
msgstr "2. The Chariot-maker "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Devalokasutta "
msgstr "18. The Realm of the Gods "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.115, sc1
msgctxt "an3.18:1.1"
msgid "“Sace vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow another path were to ask you: "

msgctxt "an3.18:1.2"
msgid "‘devalokūpapattiyā, āvuso, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussathā’ti? "
msgstr "‘Reverend, do you live the spiritual life with the ascetic Gotama so that you can be reborn in the realm of the gods?’ "

msgctxt "an3.18:1.3"
msgid "Nanu tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ puṭṭhā aṭṭīyeyyātha harāyeyyātha jiguccheyyāthā”ti? "
msgstr "Being questioned like this, wouldn’t you be horrified, repelled, and disgusted?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.18:1.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.18:1.5"
msgid "“Iti kira tumhe, bhikkhave, dibbena āyunā aṭṭīyatha harāyatha jigucchatha, dibbena vaṇṇena dibbena sukhena dibbena yasena dibbenādhipateyyena aṭṭīyatha harāyatha jigucchatha; "
msgstr "“So it seems that you are horrified, repelled, and disgusted by divine lifespan, beauty, happiness, fame, and sovereignty. "

msgctxt "an3.18:1.6"
msgid "pageva kho pana, bhikkhave, tumhehi kāyaduccaritena aṭṭīyitabbaṃ harāyitabbaṃ jigucchitabbaṃ, vacīduccaritena … manoduccaritena aṭṭīyitabbaṃ harāyitabbaṃ jigucchitabban”ti. "
msgstr "How much more then should you be horrified, embarrassed, and disgusted by bad conduct by way of body, speech, and mind.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.18:1.7"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

